          "question": "<p><a name=\"358950\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>What is the prefix expression corresponding to the expression:</p>\n\n<p>\\( \\left ( \\left ( 9+8 \\right ) \\ast 7+\\left ( 6\\ast \\left ( 5+4 \\right ) \\right )\\ast 3\\right )+2? \\)</p>\n\n<p>You may assume that \\( \\ast \\) has precedence over \\( + \\)?</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Data Structures: TIFR CSE 2021 | Part B | Question: 3</b></p>",
